main event: An observer watched a round silver colored object travel north for 5 minutes, with the object disappearing and reappearing during the observation.
interesting points: The object was described as having a metallic sound., The object appeared silvery in color., The observation lasted for 5 minutes., The object was consistent with the characteristics of an aircraft., A rising sound was heard despite the object being silent during part of the observation.
witness description: Witness observed the object continually for the duration of the sighting.
